column5: Ok, who is with me, Friday cannot get here soon enough? I have gone up north for over 15 years and every year the last week kills me, waiting to X the last few days off the calendar. 4 days (or 94 hours and 15 minutes) until launch.
Time seems to stand still. My fishing parnter owns a restaraunt/bar that has Labatt's on tap so I spend evenings there with him practicing
Hope you have a great time Hammdog. I have that same feeling and I have to wait until August. Have a safe trip!
Days feel like they have been dipped in molasses :/ Can't wait to get on the road Friday!
Only 3 days now hamm... see ya Friday! You guys may have to pick me up from the bar this year.ha!!
Ill be heading north friday night as well to get into camp saturday morning!!

Geez I cannot believe its here so soon. Four days till fishing in Canada. I have been thinking about getting packed but I better buckle down. Have to remember to pick up my Bait at Vados on Friday night.
